OL,5,G1700 Traffic Cops
OL,6,     FIn central Derbyshire, the Traffic
OL,7,     FCops are on the hunt for a car
OL,8,     Flinked to the theft of two
OL,9,     Fmotorbikes. After a 10-minute
OL,10,     Fsearch, officers spot the car.
OL,11,G1800 Police Interceptors
OL,12,     FKev and Steve go on the hunt for
OL,13,     Fheroin dealers and uncover a
OL,14,     Fshocking way to rewire your house,
OL,15,     Fwhile dog handler Liam attends the
OL,16,     Fscene of an arson attack.
OL,17,G1900 Police Interceptors
OL,18,     FJustin and Paul chase down a gang
OL,19,     Fof suspected car thieves. It takes
OL,20,     Fseven interceptors to stop a
OL,21,     Fviolent thief who tries to sink
OL,22,     Fhis teeth into them.
